It’s very God sent we must understand again

00:01:53.210 --> 00:01:55.130
the Ritambhara Pragya is working out

00:01:55.730 --> 00:01:57.850
Let him be seated somewhere.

00:01:58.130 --> 00:02:02.090
There's a guest we have, can we give a room somewhere?

00:02:12.970 --> 00:02:20.730
So, it was pointed out by Warren

00:02:20.970 --> 00:02:25.450
that he'll have to work here for two years,

00:02:25.530 --> 00:02:32.450
he cannot practice as an architect and he has to put so much money

00:02:32.530 --> 00:02:35.530
to ensure and all kinds of problems are here.

00:02:35.730 --> 00:02:39.130
And suddenly today we find somebody who is willing

00:02:39.450 --> 00:02:42.450
to take him up in India and send him abroad

00:02:42.530 --> 00:02:44.450
and all those things are there.

00:02:44.530 --> 00:02:47.490
So you can imagine how things work out for him

00:02:47.770 --> 00:02:51.210
but there should be dedication and understanding

00:02:51.770 --> 00:02:55.170
about Sahaja Yoga first of all, that’s very important.

00:02:55.690 --> 00:02:57.690
Now, today in the beginning of the whole thing

00:02:57.850 --> 00:03:03.210
I don’t want to say something that will not make you happy.

00:03:03.770 --> 00:03:10.130
Today is a day of great happiness and joy and that we have to know

00:03:10.810 --> 00:03:14.970
that Christ came on this earth

00:03:15.770 --> 00:03:20.530
to deliver us from our sins and our karmas

00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:24.970
and it was such a sacrifice

00:03:25.770 --> 00:03:32.770
He went into which we cannot see

00:03:33.250 --> 00:03:37.570
or visualize with human understanding.

00:03:38.130 --> 00:03:41.530
It was too much for a person who was so powerful

00:03:41.770 --> 00:03:46.570
to get into a position where

00:03:46.690 --> 00:03:51.450
he had to forget that he was so powerful and go through all that

00:03:51.970 --> 00:03:54.730
and treated just like an ordinary person.

00:03:55.010 --> 00:03:57.770
It was too much but he did it

00:03:58.050 --> 00:04:00.050
just because that drama was to be played

00:04:00.210 --> 00:04:03.570
because Agnya Chakra was to be opened out.

00:04:03.970 --> 00:04:07.970
But we have to understand that though he has done all that,

00:04:08.130 --> 00:04:12.530
our karmas are being taken away as you know that

00:04:12.810 --> 00:04:16.930
as soon as the kundalini is awakened, you know that

00:04:17.090 --> 00:04:21.530
kundalini cannot be awakened if your karmas aren't clean.

00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:24.890
You cannot, that’s why in the olden days

00:04:25.050 --> 00:04:28.850
people used to go to Himalayas and all those farfetched places

00:04:29.010 --> 00:04:32.930
used to clean their karmas clean their bodies clean everything

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:35.450
and then they used to get awakening of the kundalini,

00:04:35.610 --> 00:04:37.570
they used to get realization.

00:04:37.770 --> 00:04:40.050
But the way we have got realization thanks to Christ

00:04:40.210 --> 00:04:42.530
that Agnya Chakra could be opened out

00:04:42.690 --> 00:04:46.450
and that I could manage that.

00:04:46.610 --> 00:04:50.770
But we do not realize that once that is done

00:04:50.970 --> 00:04:56.170
that means you are now entitled to get your realization

00:04:56.610 --> 00:04:58.810
because of your Agnya Chakra being opened out

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:02.970
that your Sahastrara can be opened out.

00:05:03.170 --> 00:05:09.850
But, the punishment of the karmas has been taken away.

00:05:10.490 --> 00:05:13.810
You have been given such a higher position

00:05:14.170 --> 00:05:19.850
that you suddenly become Saints and you get all the knowledge

00:05:20.010 --> 00:05:23.170
that Saints cannot have about Sahaja Yoga,

00:05:23.490 --> 00:05:26.930
about the Shudha Vidya, the Nirmal Vidya,

00:05:27.090 --> 00:05:30.570
you get all the knowledge of the Spirit.

00:05:31.130 --> 00:05:40.930
But the problem is I find that we have certain special problems

00:05:41.090 --> 00:05:45.170
belonging to the special countries also

00:05:45.530 --> 00:05:50.130
and my attention has been on England very much, you know that

00:05:50.610 --> 00:05:56.170
and I have really worked here very hard, 10 years I have worked

00:05:56.850 --> 00:06:00.170
and for English Sahaja Yogis it is important to understand

00:06:00.490 --> 00:06:10.450
what are they lacking in just our own understanding of ourselves

00:06:10.530 --> 00:06:15.850
which should be done with proper critical eye

00:06:16.010 --> 00:06:19.730
so that we understand what is our problem.

00:06:20.010 --> 00:06:24.450
Of course, the karmas have been forgiven, you can see that.

00:06:24.850 --> 00:06:27.850
No problem of the karmas are there,

00:06:28.250 --> 00:06:30.770
but the problem that exists within us

00:06:30.930 --> 00:06:35.770
is also little bit from this country itself.

00:06:36.610 --> 00:06:40.490
The first is that this is a country of tamo guna

00:06:40.730 --> 00:06:43.890
because it is in a very high altitude placed

00:06:44.050 --> 00:06:47.090
and it is very cold country

00:06:47.530 --> 00:06:52.450
and people are used to drinking and all those things.

00:06:52.530 --> 00:06:57.530
So, the generations have done that, so it has gone into more tamo guna

00:06:57.730 --> 00:07:00.690
and now it is so saturated that tamo guna.

00:07:00.850 --> 00:07:03.970
When once upon a time, it was on the right side,

00:07:04.130 --> 00:07:06.010
now it has gone onto the left side

00:07:06.170 --> 00:07:10.890
because the whole saturation of that drinking and all those things

00:07:11.050 --> 00:07:16.170
have brought this tamo guna to settle down in this country.

00:07:16.770 --> 00:07:25.570
So, the first problem is of tamo and tamo guna makes you

00:07:25.850 --> 00:07:32.170
with your intelligence explain everything automatically.

00:07:33.490 --> 00:07:37.450
So, the intelligence has a capacity to cheat itself.

00:07:37.850 --> 00:07:41.010
So, the intelligence tells you – see now, all right

00:07:41.170 --> 00:07:45.170
if we have to get up in the morning that maybe all right in India

00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:50.450
but in England maybe too much (Sahaja Yogis laugh).

00:07:50.610 --> 00:07:53.970
That’s special intelligence

00:07:54.610 --> 00:08:00.450
and then you see the progress compared to other people becomes slow,

00:08:00.930 --> 00:08:03.970
despite mother is working so hard here.

00:08:05.050 --> 00:08:08.890
The second thing is that tamo gunis, you see,

00:08:09.170 --> 00:08:12.490
because they have to live with their tamo guna,

00:08:12.650 --> 00:08:17.770
they become very shallow and their depth is missing

00:08:18.250 --> 00:08:21.450
because they are on the other side of it

00:08:21.530 --> 00:08:23.050
and they do not touch their depth

00:08:23.210 --> 00:08:25.850
so they can live very superficially you see.

00:08:26.010 --> 00:08:29.130
Ah, whatever they do they don’t feel anything.

00:08:29.450 --> 00:08:31.810
They are not ashamed of it; they are not touched by it.

00:08:32.050 --> 00:08:36.890
Whatever it is, at the most they blame a bhoots of their, that’s all.

00:08:37.090 --> 00:08:39.850
But otherwise in a shallow everyone.

00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:43.530
They do not touch it that much where they should touch

00:08:43.730 --> 00:08:45.930
because of tamo guna.

00:08:46.170 --> 00:08:51.090
Now, as it is this is the heart of the Universe

00:08:52.490 --> 00:08:57.810
and a person who has a heart is the most deep personality

00:08:58.770 --> 00:09:00.810
because you see doing with the heart.

00:09:01.050 --> 00:09:04.450
Anything done with the heart means you are all out for it.

00:09:04.770 --> 00:09:08.530
So just the other way around it is that sometimes when we are shallow,

00:09:08.730 --> 00:09:16.130
there's no heart, nothing, we do something without the heart.

00:09:16.570 --> 00:09:21.210
Now, as you have seen in the Ashtanga Yogas,

00:09:21.610 --> 00:09:25.770
there is a many a times I have said Ishvara Pranidhana is the first.

00:09:26.010 --> 00:09:29.610
Now what is Ishvara Pranidhana, we must understand.

00:09:30.170 --> 00:09:37.450
Ishvara Pranidhana is the establishment of God in your heart.

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:40.250
Now, how do you do?

00:09:40.570 --> 00:09:46.450
You see, you see a mantra, you are just saying it outwardly.

00:09:46.730 --> 00:09:52.090
You are clearing out outwardly. You are meditating outwardly.

00:09:52.770 --> 00:09:57.170
But when you are saying that,

00:09:57.490 --> 00:10:02.650
you are just using your right side

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:08.810
or your left side but not your heart.

00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:12.650
So, what you have to do is to balance it.

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:17.770
When you are saying something, say it with devotion, with dedication,

00:10:18.130 --> 00:10:22.650
with understanding and try to put it in your heart that

00:10:23.170 --> 00:10:32.970
"Whatever I am saying is a mantra given to me by Adi Shakti herself."

00:10:33.170 --> 00:10:36.130
So is a mantra very powerful.

00:10:36.530 --> 00:10:38.890
But the mantras also lose their powers

00:10:39.050 --> 00:10:41.810
if you do not have the Ishvara Pranidhana.

00:10:42.170 --> 00:10:46.450
That means your Ishvara must be established in your heart

00:10:47.170 --> 00:10:50.450
and this is what we lack is that when we do something

00:10:50.530 --> 00:10:54.450
we just do outwardly in a shallow manner.

00:10:54.530 --> 00:10:57.530
And if you are shallow you will be playing with this.

00:10:57.770 --> 00:11:00.450
Now playing games is a very common thing with us

00:11:00.610 --> 00:11:03.450
because you see people with Tamasa what else will they do.

00:11:03.610 --> 00:11:05.770
I mean they are lazy lumps.

00:11:05.970 --> 00:11:09.450
So, the mind has to be used. You see, mind doesn’t stop, isn’t it?

00:11:09.610 --> 00:11:12.970
It's working all the time and we are lazy, doing nothing.

00:11:13.210 --> 00:11:17.450
So, the mind plays on its own and then we should understand that

00:11:17.530 --> 00:11:20.450
this mind is the one that makes you shallow.

00:11:20.610 --> 00:11:23.970
We make faces as if we are very happy before mother

00:11:24.130 --> 00:11:25.450
or something like that

00:11:25.530 --> 00:11:28.450
or we say we are very this thing and we have achieved this and that

00:11:28.530 --> 00:11:31.450
suppose but she knows.

00:11:31.530 --> 00:11:38.850
So, what we have to do is to feel what we want to say,

00:11:39.570 --> 00:11:40.450
what we have to do.

00:11:40.530 --> 00:11:45.610
That is Ishvara Pranidhana. It should not be superficial.

00:11:45.770 --> 00:11:49.930
I have seen people, Oh Mother! This that this that.

00:11:50.210 --> 00:11:54.530
Just coming from the lips only sometimes.

00:11:55.170 --> 00:11:57.450
It should come from the heart.

00:11:57.530 --> 00:12:01.450
Try to feel that. You will see the joy will be much more.

00:12:01.530 --> 00:12:05.650
You're trying to give me joy. You try to give yourself that joy.

00:12:05.810 --> 00:12:08.650
That’s what you are feeling within your heart.

00:12:09.090 --> 00:12:11.770
Try to feel that in your heart.

00:12:11.970 --> 00:12:15.050
When the Ishvara Pranidhana is established.

00:12:15.490 --> 00:12:20.530
But this is one of the problems is the Tamasa.

00:12:20.970 --> 00:12:24.770
But when they were aggressive in this country then their aggression

00:12:24.930 --> 00:12:29.450
you see they created another problem is to sort of a condition our minds.

00:12:29.610 --> 00:12:32.450
This also we should face directly.

00:12:32.610 --> 00:12:36.450
Specially for Britishers, it is important to face that, very important

00:12:36.530 --> 00:12:40.890
because I have been noticing it is happening. Now what happens?

00:12:41.450 --> 00:12:44.450
Supposing, you are an aggressor means what do you do?

00:12:44.530 --> 00:12:46.010
I would see in a stark way,

00:12:46.170 --> 00:12:49.450
just forget that you are Britisher just go away from it.

00:12:49.530 --> 00:12:56.610
