and you go and attack another person, driving him out of his house,

00:13:00.530 --> 00:13:08.170
stay there nicely for 300 years. It is that. As simple as that.

00:13:08.530 --> 00:13:11.530
That’s what the forefathers have done here

00:13:11.810 --> 00:13:15.450
and they have conditioned our mind, means what have we done.

00:13:15.530 --> 00:13:19.450
That means you have no respect for anybody else's culture.

00:13:20.770 --> 00:13:22.770
Simple as that.

00:13:22.970 --> 00:13:26.930
That they showed no respect for anybody else's life.

00:13:27.490 --> 00:13:30.450
To them, they were the ones that could occupy other countries,

00:13:30.530 --> 00:13:35.130
they could capture other countries and live there, dominate there.

00:13:37.890 --> 00:13:42.130
But as a result of that the conditioning is still in the minds

00:13:42.770 --> 00:13:48.970
because when we live, say in the ashram - I was very happy to know

00:13:49.130 --> 00:13:54.450
that the ashram of Brighton is looking so much better,

00:13:55.570 --> 00:13:58.930
people are looking after, is a very big thing

00:13:59.090 --> 00:14:01.970
that shows that you respect.

00:14:02.250 --> 00:14:07.130
That place which is a holy place you are looking after it.

