respects anybody’s wife or anybody’s husband. They are married

00:15:38.890 --> 00:15:42.690
but their eyes will be on somebody’s wife, somebody's husband.

00:15:43.490 --> 00:15:48.450
How can you do that? See to the subtle side,

00:15:48.530 --> 00:15:50.570
because now you have become subtler people

00:15:50.770 --> 00:15:54.450
and you must see these problems exist in our country

00:15:54.530 --> 00:15:59.050
that we have got this conditioning around us is all this going on.

00:15:59.530 --> 00:16:04.730
Somebody’s wife is going with somebody’s husband. No respect.

00:16:05.170 --> 00:16:09.450
They are married people, how can you carry on with somebody’s wife

00:16:09.530 --> 00:16:11.570
or somebody’s husband.

00:16:11.810 --> 00:16:15.130
Just think of the society in which we live. Isn’t it?

00:16:15.490 --> 00:16:17.890
Now somebody is married to someone,

00:16:18.650 --> 00:16:25.570
now you cannot carry on with a person who belongs to somebody else.

00:16:26.090 --> 00:16:28.530
Is a simple thing like that.

00:16:28.930 --> 00:16:33.450
But is all, you see in the society you live in that kind of a society.

00:16:33.890 --> 00:16:36.170
I mean every day we have here such news,

00:16:36.490 --> 00:16:38.650
I mean it’s just shocking sometimes.

00:16:38.890 --> 00:16:40.170
So, we have to face the problems with which you are living

00:16:40.490 --> 00:16:41.930
like Indians have their own problems

00:16:42.490 --> 00:16:44.850
and they are horrid on that line.

00:16:45.050 --> 00:16:48.450
So, we have to face our problems so first of all we have to know

00:16:48.530 --> 00:16:51.770
that we must establish the Ishvara Pranidhana.

00:16:52.130 --> 00:16:55.930
Sahaja Yoga cannot be established by people who are shallow,

00:16:56.210 --> 00:16:58.530
who are superficially in Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:58.850 --> 00:17:00.730
Some people think they can play about,

00:17:00.890 --> 00:17:04.650
they feel happy by disturbing the ashramites,

00:17:04.810 --> 00:17:07.530
by talking against the ashram people about Sahaja Yogis,

00:17:07.730 --> 00:17:09.010
many I have seen,

00:17:09.170 --> 00:17:13.210
Sahaja Yogis are a horrid people as if other people are better.

00:17:14.530 --> 00:17:19.450
They go on like that playing. Now, what is the thing they lose.

00:17:19.530 --> 00:17:21.890
They are the losers. They don’t understand this.

00:17:22.170 --> 00:17:25.570
By doing this kind of a thing you are the loser.

00:17:25.890 --> 00:17:29.570
Whom are you playing with? You are playing against with yourself.

00:17:29.850 --> 00:17:34.570
Those people who try to criticize Sahaja yogis must know that

00:17:34.770 --> 00:17:39.450
they are cutting themselves out of Sahaja Yoga.

00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:45.530
