00:17:47.810 --> 00:17:51.690
Nobody should criticize Sahaja Yogis which is a group.

00:17:51.850 --> 00:17:55.770
One individual Sahaja Yogi is doing wrong, I will know.

00:17:55.930 --> 00:18:01.450
So, it is very important that you should be accepted by the group.

00:18:01.650 --> 00:18:04.450
If you are an individual and think you are a great personality

00:18:04.530 --> 00:18:07.130
and you are trying to correct others,

00:18:07.970 --> 00:18:10.690
and say that the Sahaja Yogis are bad and the ashram is bad

00:18:10.850 --> 00:18:12.490
and do like that

00:18:13.610 --> 00:18:17.450
then you must know you are getting out of Sahaja Yoga.

00:18:17.770 --> 00:18:23.850
Very soon you will be out. So, one should not try these things

00:18:24.050 --> 00:18:26.450
and taking sides with newcomers.

00:18:26.610 --> 00:18:29.450
When the newcomers are coming you are more attached to the newcomers

00:18:29.530 --> 00:18:33.530
than to the Sahaja Yogis, then be sure you are not there.

00:18:34.770 --> 00:18:36.730
That’s one of the ways you can judge.

00:18:36.970 --> 00:18:42.450
Are you with the collectivity or are you trying to get out of it

00:18:42.530 --> 00:18:46.450
and trying to control all the rest?

00:18:46.730 --> 00:18:50.450
All right, this is one of the ways of understanding yourself.

00:18:50.530 --> 00:18:54.850
All such tricks will put you out of Sahaja Yoga

00:18:57.570 --> 00:19:01.170
and I think this is what Pluto is working out now.

00:19:01.490 --> 00:19:04.450
So, we should be very careful. It’s nice to celebrate,

00:19:04.530 --> 00:19:06.730
but spirituality is purity.

00:19:06.890 --> 00:19:10.450
If your heart is not pure, you'll be thrown out.

00:19:13.530 --> 00:19:21.130
Pluto is purity and purity has one quality that it is very joy-giving.

00:19:21.730 --> 00:19:25.450
It's glorious to be pure to be innocent

00:19:25.530 --> 00:19:30.450
but it also means that many things have to be dropped out

00:19:30.610 --> 00:19:34.690
and those who don’t drop out will be dropped out with those things.

00:19:35.050 --> 00:19:39.450
So, I want to warn you that it’s a very good day that I started today.

00:19:40.130 --> 00:19:44.170
But this is the problem we'll be facing now so be very careful,

00:19:44.490 --> 00:19:49.770
don’t play games with Sahaja Yoga. Clean your heart.

00:19:50.010 --> 00:19:53.650
This is from few people I know who are doing these things.

00:19:53.890 --> 00:19:56.450
I know about every one of them.

